$ ORA-01017: invalid username/password; logon denied

{ Changing a user's password

  In case a → development/databases/Oracle/users-roles/users has forgot the password, another privileged user can assign a new password with
code {
alter user peter_mayer identified by theNewPassword;
code }

}

